{"tid":2429962,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"點解Adobe premiere pro冇啦啦冇聲？","createTime":"2021-03-02T15:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T18:09:57.000Z","uid":134466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b74cf71a191c5731aabcbfac7e79a8755f74d2f7","tid":2429962,"uid":134466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"唔知點解條聲檔啲聲有啲問題，但係電腦播同埋拉有畫面嘅影片又冇問題，試過拉其他聲檔都係有問題。<br />\n條聲檔有10秒咁，當我拉入pr 之後，佢將我條聲後5秒嘅內容拉前左取代左前5秒，之後原來後面個5秒就變左靜音（如圖咁，後面空左），可以點處理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3tHhpj5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3tHhpj5.jpg&h=d615a66d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cda4e9f811e78a21b3173ce087f3e1e169eb801","tid":2429962,"uid":134466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"岩岩發現放其他聲檔又冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係個條有問題，但係我頭先仲剪得好地地，第一次個陣仲有前半part,依加突然冇左前半part<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc9a76369431b3843f84ea2e74b40479c04280b","tid":2429962,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"翻版係咁<br />\n比錢買正版啦"},{"pid":"7b6cf6204490635f20b8649433c72109601d9fb3","tid":2429962,"uid":156109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:54:47.000Z","msg":"轉格式"},{"pid":"69c2b73c1bb816cdfb2160b8491887b39332fe00","tid":2429962,"uid":202428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T18:09:57.000Z","msg":"一係peak file未generate完<br />\n如果唔係就用media encoder轉咗format先用"}]}